WEBVTT

00:03:26.399 --> 00:03:30.641
But I listened for her check-ins
every few minutes.

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:32.958
I didn't know Richard.

00:03:33.839 --> 00:03:36.728
But it mattered to me that he survived.

00:03:38.752 --> 00:03:40.546
All I shared with them

00:03:40.570 --> 00:03:42.053
was my first name.

00:03:43.013 --> 00:03:44.164
They didn't know

00:03:44.188 --> 00:03:47.711
that I was a head of a department
at the Design Council.

00:03:49.185 --> 00:03:52.742
And here is my beloved briefcase,

00:03:52.766 --> 00:03:55.217
also rescued from that morning.

00:03:56.479 --> 00:04:00.445
They didn't know that I published
architecture and design journals,